<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.8">
<l>pāṭōmē yentai perumāṉai pāṭiniṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṭōmē yāyiram pērāṉai pērniṉaintu</l>
<l>cūṭōmē cūṭun tuḻāyalaṅkal cūṭinām</l>
<l>kūṭōmē kūṭak kuṟippākil naṉṉeñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do we not sing of the lord, our father? Do we not dance,</l>
<l>Continually singing his one-thousand names? Thinking of his names,</l>
<l>Do we not wear the tulasī garland [he] wore? Wearing [that],</l>
<l>Will we not we join him if [his] aim is to join [us], good heart?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
